# SmartPave: Road Condition & Pothole Analysis

## 📌 Overview
This project detects potholes and analyzes road conditions using machine learning.

## 🚀 Features
- Pothole detection
- Road condition scoring
- Real-time alert system
- Graph visualization (loss & precision)

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Python
- OpenCV
- YOLO
- Streamlit

## 📊 Dataset
- Trained on 1300 images

## 📈 Output
- Detection results
- Performance graphs
